== Introduction ==

Many of the packages developed under the {{project_name_long}} umbrella can be thought of as independent projects in their own right. They are directly relevant to Debian hosts because they can increase security or usability.

This guide shows how to download these select packages from the {{project_name_long}} repository; they can be downloaded stand-alone or combined.

